  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Pure Brilliance</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Pure Brilliance</b> is a resource exclusive to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i>, introduced in <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/From_Beyond\" title=\"From Beyond\">From Beyond</a></i>. It is obtained by mining <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ryftstal\" title=\"Ryftstal\">Ryftstals</a> that spawn from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Rift\" title=\"Lunar Rift\">Lunar Rifts</a>.\n</p><p>Pure Brilliance is used to craft the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Brightsmithy\" title=\"Brightsmithy\">Brightsmithy</a> and all of the items craftable at said station.\n</p><p><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wilson/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Wilson/Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Wilson</a> with the <span class=\"dark-invert\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Innovator\" title=\"Lunar Innovator\"><img alt=\"Lunar Innovator.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Lunar_Innovator.png/24px-Lunar_Innovator.png?300f2d\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\"></a></span> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Innovator\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lunar Innovator\">Lunar Innovator</a> Skill can craft 1 Pure Brilliance with 3 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Infused_Moon_Shard\" title=\"Infused Moon Shard\">Infused Moon Shards</a>, as well as use 1 Pure Brilliance to craft 2 Infused Moon Shards. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Pure Brilliance was introduced in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/From_Beyond#Taking_Root\" title=\"From Beyond\">Taking Root</a></i> update.</li>\n<li>The opposite of this item is <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Horror\" title=\"Pure Horror\">Pure Horror</a>.</li>\n<li>Pure Brilliance is a play on words as the word Brilliance pertains to both high intelligence and intense luminescence.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Assets\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Research_Notes\" title=\"Research Notes\"><img alt=\"Research Notes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Research_Notes.png/32px-Research_Notes.png?ef2da4\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Assets</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Pure_Brilliance_Dropped_Idle.gif\" class=\"image\" title=\"Idle animation\"><img alt=\"Idle animation\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Pure_Brilliance_Dropped_Idle.gif/120px-Pure_Brilliance_Dropped_Idle.gif?6be614\" width=\"120\" height=\"119\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Idle animation</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Resources-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Brilliance#Resources-0\">Resources</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Craftable_Items-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Brilliance#Craftable_Items-0\">Craftable Items</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
